exemplo na pasta json-server-exemplo


json server
Usa um arquivo JSON com dados mocados para simular um servi√ßo REST.
https://www.npmjs.com/package/json-server
https://medium.com/letsboot/the-perfect-mock-backend-to-start-with-an-angular-application-3d751d16614f

npm install --save-dev json-server

./node_modules/.bin/json-server --version
./node_modules/.bin/json-server --help
./node_modules/.bin/json-server --watch ./mock/db.json --port 3004

mudar o id para usar no get
./node_modules/.bin/json-server --watch ./mock/db.json --port 3004 --i name